Software Quality Awards 2019

Three Cheers for 3 Innovative S/W Quality Award-Winning Solutions

#Robert Bosch Engineering and Business Solutions

August 12, 2020
5
    • 2

      Quality doesnt happen by accident Robert Bosch

      It is truly a proud and unforgettable moment for teams in RBEI and RBVH who were an integral part of team CI that won the 2019 Bosch Software Quality Award for 3 innovative custom solutions crafted for BBM, namely oneQ, myTime and Calculation Suite. The Bosch Quality awards ceremony was livestreamed on July 17, 2020, with the board of management in attendance physically and the award winners connected virtually from different parts of the world. The Bosch Quality Awards program was co-hosted by G1 and G11. The award was received by Heinzmann Horst (CI/DAP3.4 CI/DAP3-iGPM along with 4 colleagues, Jin Dan (M/BDX-CS M/QMM), Formela Marcin (CI/DAP3.9), Schwarz Dana (CI/DAP3.6), & Sattler Marcel (CI/DAP3.5) on behalf of the entire team.

      This outstanding achievement was certainly achieved through uncompromising quality, technical perfection and reliability of the 3 iGPM solutions. With a customer base of 50,000 globally, all three solutions are aimed at increasing BBM effectiveness and cross division collaboration through integrated processes providing customer satisfaction, value addition and technical excellence.

      Here is an overview of the 3 solutions:

      As said by Dr. Volkmar Denner, Chairman, Board of Management, Since go-live, they have had very good internal customer feedback and only a very low number of tickets. With an outstanding test strategy, clean design and development environment, they achieved an excellent CDQ assessment and the highest possible score in fulfillment of the software quality assessment criteria.

      No doubt, winning an award for quality requires top-notch software quality and highest customer satisfaction. So, it is indeed a very proud moment for all the teams involved. With 58 team members from RBEI and 12 from RBVH, iGPM is the largest collaboration program with CI. Congratulations to the team spread across India, Vietnam and Germany for setting an example for CI and RBEI co-operation with high trust levels leading to very good quality deliverables and customer delight. The teams have been putting in hard work and working as ONE team! said Raghuram Joshi, Practice head, RBEI/BSX.

      So, what went behind the scenes to innovate the award-winning state-of-the-art solutions?
